data.description: LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION! Check out this beautiful 4 sided brick home located in Meansville. Just minutes from the schools and downtown. This charming 4 bedroom, 1.5 bath home has new LVP flooring through out, with an open concept. The kitchen has just been renovated with a large island, stainless steal appliances and easy access to the huge covered back porch! Cozy up on the couch in the living room with the fireplace and enjoy some Sunday football. The back yard is fenced in, and includes a large storage shed/workshop. Enjoy your mornings or evenings sitting outside on your back porch or entertaining friends and family.
